lead_paragraph: Bayern Munich are expecting PSV Eindhoven to provide much stiffer opposition on home soil on Tuesday after having swept past the Dutch side 4-1 at the Allianz Arena earlier this month.

headline.print_headline: PSV Will Be Much Tougher This Time, Says Ancelotti
headline.main: PSV Will Be Much Tougher This Time, Says Ancelotti
